regents week seemed pretty easy for most people but stressful for me. to top it all off i went to boston for the weekend thinking it was going to be a somewhat relaxing trip...not.

then i got a call at 4 from the fucking watermill telling me i had to come in at 5! gaaa! so i worked till 10:30, came home, got dressed, and went to josh' house. iofhdhhdgh... nicest house ever...?

anywoo, i think today im going to monks and pauls swim meet with claire. shall me fun.

peaceeee

got my car. that was fun. i guess i can start to drive to school on tuesday.
